### =================================================================
### 圆锥角膜诊断平台 - 完整接口测试文件
### 使用方法：在 IDEA 中打开，点击每个请求左侧的 ▶ 运行
### 基础 URL: http://localhost:8080
### 注意：patient_id 是业务主键（字符串），格式如 "P20240501"
### =================================================================

### ======================== 1. 患者管理 /api/patients ========================

### [P1] 新增患者（完整字段）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "name": "李明",
  "gender": "Male",
  "dateOfBirth": "1998-03-15",
  "age": 28,
  "idCard": "350102199803150011",
  "contact": "13800138001",
  "address": "福建省厦门市思明区",
  "medicalHistory": "无过敏史，否认高血压、糖尿病等慢性病史"
}

### [P2] 新增患者（最简字段，仅必填项）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P20260531",
  "name": "王芳"
}

### [P3] 查询所有患者
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients
Accept: application/json

### [P4] 按姓名模糊搜索
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients?name=李
Accept: application/json

### [P5] 按 ID 查询单个患者
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients/P20260530
Accept: application/json

### [P6] 更新患者信息
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/patients/P20260530
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "name": "李明（更新）",
  "gender": "Male",
  "age": 29,
  "contact": "13900139001",
  "address": "福建省福州市鼓楼区"
}

### [P7] 删除患者（级联删除角膜检查、影像、病历）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/patients/P20260531

### -------- 异常测试 --------

### [P8] 重复创建同一 patientId（期望 400: Patient ID already exists）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "name": "重复ID测试"
}

### [P9] 查询不存在的患者（期望 400: Patient not found）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/patients/P_NOT_EXIST
Accept: application/json

### [P10] 缺少必填 patientId（期望 400: Patient ID cannot be empty）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "缺少ID"
}

### ======================== 2. 角膜检查 /api/exams ========================

### [E1] 新增角膜检查（含地形图和生物力学参数）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/exams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "examDate": "2026-05-30",
  "eyeSide": "right",
  "examType": "Pentacam",
  "diagnosis": "疑似早期圆锥角膜",
  "topography": {
    "frontK1": 45.23,
    "frontK2": 47.56,
    "frontKm": 46.39,
    "frontRf": 7.45,
    "frontRs": 7.10,
    "frontRm": 7.27,
    "frontQVal": -0.25,
    "frontAstig": 2.33,
    "frontAxis": 85.0,
    "backK1": -6.12,
    "backK2": -6.89,
    "backKm": -6.50,
    "backRf": 6.38,
    "backRs": 6.01,
    "backRm": 6.19,
    "thinnestLocatPachyX": 485.0,
    "thinnestLocatPachyY": -2.1,
    "corneaVolume": 61.2,
    "acDepth": 3.12,
    "iop": 15.5,
    "pupilDia": 4.5
  },
  "biomechanics": {
    "ccbi": 0.8523,
    "ctbi": 0.7810,
    "isValue": 1.2500,
    "spA1": 89.5,
    "integrRadius": 7.85,
    "arth": 385.2,
    "daRatio": 1.62,
    "ssi": 0.95
  }
}

### [E2] 新增角膜检查（仅必填字段，无参数）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/exams
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "examDate": "2026-05-30",
  "eyeSide": "left",
  "examType": "Corvis_TBI"
}

### [E3] 按患者ID查询所有检查记录（将 P20260530 替换为实际ID）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/exams?patientId=P20260530
Accept: application/json

### [E4] 按检查ID查询单条记录（将 1 替换为实际 exam_id）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/exams/1
Accept: application/json

### [E5] 更新检查记录（将 1 替换为实际 exam_id）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/exams/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "examId": 1,
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "examDate": "2026-05-30",
  "eyeSide": "right",
  "examType": "Pentacam",
  "diagnosis": "顿挫型圆锥角膜 (Forme Fruste KC)"
}

### [E6] 删除检查记录（将 1 替换为实际 exam_id）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/exams/1

### ======================== 3. 医学影像 /api/images ========================

### [I1] 登记影像信息（路径方式，不含二进制数据）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/images
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "examId": 1,
  "imageType": "Pentacam",
  "eyeSide": "right",
  "imagePath": "/data/images/p20260530/pentacam_right_20260530.jpg",
  "fileName": "pentacam_right_20260530.jpg",
  "fileSize": 2048000
}

### [I2] 按患者ID查询影像列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/images?patientId=P20260530
Accept: application/json

### [I3] 按检查ID查询影像列表（将 1 替换为实际 exam_id）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/images?examId=1
Accept: application/json

### [I4] 删除影像（将 1 替换为实际 image_id）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/images/1

### [I5] 不传任何参数（期望 400: Either patientId or examId is required）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/images
Accept: application/json

### ======================== 4. 病历记录 /api/records ========================

### [R1] 新增病历
POST http://localhost:8080/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "visitDate": "2026-05-30",
  "chiefComplaint": "右眼视力下降3个月，偶有视物重影",
  "presentIllness": "患者自述3月前无明显诱因出现右眼视力下降，伴轻度视物变形",
  "pastHistory": "无高血压、糖尿病史，无眼部外伤史",
  "physicalExam": "右眼裸眼视力0.4，矫正视力0.6；角膜中央轻度隆起变薄",
  "diagnosis": "右眼圆锥角膜（早期/顿挫型）",
  "leftEyeDiagnosis": "正常",
  "rightEyeDiagnosis": "顿挫型圆锥角膜 (Forme Fruste KC)",
  "treatmentPlan": "1. 右眼角膜胶原交联术(CXL)评估\n2. 定期随访角膜地形图每6个月",
  "doctorNotes": "建议完善Corvis ST生物力学检查及前节OCT",
  "doctorName": "陈主任"
}

### [R2] 按患者ID查询病历列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/records?patientId=P20260530
Accept: application/json

### [R3] 按病历ID查询单条记录（将 1 替换为实际 record_id）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/records/1
Accept: application/json

### [R4] 更新病历（将 1 替换为实际 record_id）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/records/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recordId": 1,
  "patientId": "P20260530",
  "visitDate": "2026-05-30",
  "diagnosis": "确诊圆锥角膜 KC Grade I",
  "treatmentPlan": "已行右眼角膜胶原交联术(CXL)",
  "doctorName": "陈主任"
}

### [R5] 删除病历（将 1 替换为实际 record_id）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/records/1
